item.title: Molecular Detection and Characterization of Highly Pathogenic H5N1 Avian Influenza Viruses in Wild Birds Inhabiting Western Alaska Provides Evidence for Three Independent Viral Introductions
item.description: Abstract This data set describes three independent viral introductions of Highly pathogenic H5N1 avian influenza viruses into Alaska. Access Points https://alaska.usgs.gov/products/data.php?dataid=606
